Package ch.zhaw.einhoerner.editor

Class ParsedInput

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.zhaw.einhoerner.editor.ParsedInput
  • public class ParsedInput
extends java.lang.Object
    This class holds all information that was parsed from a user input. It consists of - a command that has been detected from the user input - the command's parameter list (can be empty) - an (optional) text which follows the last parameter For an exact manual, please consult the Wiki-Page on our GitHub Repository.
